{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-22T12:32:11.340Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Grid Search is an "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "exhaustive brute-force hyperparameter tuning technique"}, {"type": "text", "text": " that systematically evaluates every possible combination of pre-specified hyperparameter values to find the combination that yields the best model performance on a validation set. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://h2o.ai/wiki/grid-search/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "h2o"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Grid Search — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What it is"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "In hyperparameter tuning, Grid Search constructs a multidimensional \"grid\" where:\n- Each dimension represents one hyperparameter (e.g., learning rate, number of layers, batch size)\n- Each point on the grid represents one specific combination of hyperparameter values\n- The algorithm trains and evaluates a separate model for every grid point"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "For example, if you specify:\n- Learning rate: {0.01, 0.1, 0.5} (3 values)\n- Number of hidden layers: {2, 4} (2 values)"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Grid Search will train "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "3 × 4 = 6 models"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (one for each combination) and select the best."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why it matters in Generative AI Core Architectures"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Generative AI models (like Transformers, GANs, and diffusion models) have complex architectures with many critical hyperparameters:"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hyperparameter Category"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Examples in Generative AI"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Architecture"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Number of layers, hidden dimension size, attention heads"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Training"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Learning rate, batch size, gradient clipping threshold"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Optimization"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Weight decay, EMA decay rate, warmup steps"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Generation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Temperature, top-k/top-p sampling, maxLength"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Grid Search ensures you "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "explore the entire specified search space"}, {"type": "text", "text": " without missing the optimal combination, giving high confidence in your final model's performance."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "How it works (step-by-step)"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Define the grid"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Specify which hyperparameters to tune and discrete values for each"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Generate combinations"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Create all possible combinations (Cartesian product)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Train models"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": For each combination, train the model from scratch"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Evaluate"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Use cross-validation or a validation set to measure performance"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Select best"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Choose the hyperparameter set with the highest validation score"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Final model"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Train the final model with the optimal hyperparameters"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The total number of models to train is:\n\\[\nN"}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}], "text": "{\\text{models}} = \\prod"}, {"type": "text", "text": "{i=1}^{k} n_i\n\\]\nwhere "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "k"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the number of hyperparameters and "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "n_i"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the number of values for hyperparameter "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "i"}}, {"type": "text", "text": "."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefits"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Advantage"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Explanation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Exhaustive"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Guarantees finding the best combination within your specified grid "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://h2o.ai/wiki/grid-search/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "h2o"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Simple & deterministic"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Easy to implement, understand, and reproduce"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Fully parallelizable"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Each model train is independent—run across multiple GPUs/machines"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Automated"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Minimizes manual intervention in tuning"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Trade-offs and limitations"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Limitation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Impact on Generative AI"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Computationally expensive"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Training one Transformer can take days; grid search might require hundreds of runs "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://h2o.ai/wiki/grid-search/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "h2o"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Exponential scaling"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "5 hyperparameters with 6 values each = "}, {"type": "inlineMath", "attrs": {"latex": "6^{5} = 7,776"}}, {"type": "text", "text": " models"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Requires discrete values"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Must guess which values to test; may miss optimal values between grid points "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://h2o.ai/wiki/grid-search/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "h2o"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Poor for large search spaces"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Unsuitable for high-dimensional data or many hyperparameters"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "When to use Grid Search vs. alternatives"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Use Grid Search when:"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- You have "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "few hyperparameters"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (2–4) with "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "narrow ranges"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- Training each model is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "relatively fast"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (simple models or small datasets)\n- You need "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "guaranteed coverage"}, {"type": "text", "text": " of the search space"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Use alternatives (Random Search, Bayesian Optimization, evolutionary methods) when:"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- You have "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "many hyperparameters"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (5+) with "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "broad ranges"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- Training is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "extremely expensive"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (large neural networks, days per run)\n- You need "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "efficient exploration"}, {"type": "text", "text": " with fewer training runs"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "For large Generative AI models (LLMs, diffusion models), "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Random Search"}, {"type": "text", "text": " or "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Bayesian Optimization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " are often preferred because they sample intelligently rather than exhaustively, saving weeks of compute time."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Practical example in code (scikit-learn style)"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "from sklearn.model_selection import GridSearchCV\n\nparam_grid = {\n    'learning_rate': [0.001, 0.01, 0.1],\n    'num_layers': [2, 4, 6],\n    'batch_size': [32, 64]\n}\n\ngrid_search = GridSearchCV(\n    estimator=your_generator_model(),\n    param_grid=param_grid,\n    cv=5,  # 5-fold cross-validation\n    n_jobs=-1  # Use all available CPUs\n)\n\ngrid_search.fit(X_train, y_train)\nbest_params = grid_search.best_params_"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key takeaways"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Grid Search is "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "exhaustive and deterministic"}, {"type": "text", "text": "—it tests every combination you specify "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://h2o.ai/wiki/grid-search/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "h2o"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "It's "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "simple to use"}, {"type": "text", "text": " but "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "computationally expensive"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", especially for large generative models "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://h2o.ai/wiki/grid-search/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "h2o"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The number of models grows "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "exponentially"}, {"type": "text", "text": " with hyperparameters and values"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "For "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Core Architectures"}, {"type": "text", "text": " in Generative AI, it's practical only for small-scale experiments; production LLMs typically use more efficient methods"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "You must "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "predefine discrete values"}, {"type": "text", "text": "—it cannot discover optimal values outside your grid "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "https://h2o.ai/wiki/grid-search/", "target": "_blank", "rel": "noopener noreferrer nofollow", "class": "text-brand-600 underline dark:text-brand-400", "title": null}}], "text": "h2o"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Grid Search is foundational for understanding hyperparameter tuning, but in practice, modern Generative AI workflows often combine it with "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "coarse-to-fine strategies"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (wide grid first, then refined search around best results) or switch to "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Bayesian Optimization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for expensive models."}]}]}}